        div#projects-wrapper.content-wrapper
            div#projects.content-spacing.content-marker
            div.sidebar-spacing.content-div
            div.content-cell.content-div.hidden
                div#projects-container.content-container
                    div#projects-list-container
                        div#projects-title.content-title PROJECTS
                        div#projects-description.content-text I’ve had a chance to work on some truly interesting projects over the years. This includes things such as autonomous sailboats, self-balancing robots, personal webpage, etc. This section highlights some of the most memorable and important ones that I’ve worked on. Non-mobile users can hover over each image for a short clip of the project.
                        div.list-container
                            ul
                                li.project-item
                                    div.project-image
                                        video(loop muted preload data-url="./videos/sailbot.mp4").project-video
                                        img(src="./images/index/sailbot.jpg" alt="UBC Sailbot").pixelated
                                        div.load-circle-container.circle-load
